      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a practical choice for a budget-conscious buyer seeking dependable transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who values value over cosmetics, but it still offers solid potential as a daily driver, backup vehicle, or project. A sensible opportunity to get behind the wheel without stretching your budget.",
