    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels that gets the job done? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a great little project to tinker with. It\u2019s got plenty of character, starts up, and offers real value for the money. If you\u2019re after something cheap, honest, and ready for its next chapter, this could be a great fit.",
