      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with plenty of life left in the platform. Engine starts up and pulls through the rev range, transmission engages as it should, and the chassis still feels planted enough to enjoy around town. Not a show car and it has the wear you\u2019d expect, but for someone looking for inexpensive transportation or a hands-on project, this is a straightforward, mechanically honest car with good bones. Priced to move and worth a look if you want something usable today with room to improve over time.",
