      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left in it? This car is a straightforward, budget-friendly option that\u2019s great for someone who wants basic transport or a project to tinker with. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s got character, and at this price it\u2019s a chance to get on the road without breaking the bank. If you\u2019re after honest value and something you can make your own, this one\u2019s worth a look.",
